      <title>拉马福萨宣誓就任南非总统</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/south-african-election-ramaphosa-sworn-in-for-new-term</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西里尔·拉马福萨宣誓就任南非总统三周前，选举剥夺了他所在政党的议会多数席位，并迫使其与长期竞争对手结成权力分享联盟。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/south-african-election-ramaphosa-sworn-in-for-new-term</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 10:27:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国利差扩大，一年后损失 8 亿欧元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/france-sees-wider-spreads-costing-800-million-after-a-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国财政部估计，总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙宣布提前举行立法选举后，法国债务遭到抛售，如果高额借贷成本持续一年，法国将蒙受约 8 亿欧元（8.59 亿美元）的额外损失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/france-sees-wider-spreads-costing-800-million-after-a-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 10:10:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>勒庞的政党支持武装乌克兰，称“不会派遣法国军队”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/le-pen-s-party-backs-arming-ukraine-says-no-french-troops</link>
      <description><![CDATA[玛丽娜·勒庞所在国民联盟党主席乔丹·巴德拉表示，他赞成向乌克兰提供自卫所需的弹药，但不会提供可能引发更大规模战争的装备，这与法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙在法国在冲突中的作用上的立场相对接近。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/le-pen-s-party-backs-arming-ukraine-says-no-french-troops</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 10:09:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场关注法国和意大利因赤字问题受到欧盟谴责</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/france-and-italy-get-eu-scolding-for-deficits-as-markets-watch</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国和意大利因巨额赤字而受到欧盟的谴责，这是对抗的第一阶段，将考验欧盟的决心，理论上可能引发数十亿欧元的罚款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/france-and-italy-get-eu-scolding-for-deficits-as-markets-watch</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 09:37:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>顾问称乌克兰欢迎俄罗斯参加下次峰会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/ukraine-open-to-see-russia-at-next-summit-zelenskiy-key-aide-yermak-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰总统泽连斯基的幕僚长表示，乌克兰可能会邀请俄罗斯参加与国际伙伴举行的下一次会议，旨在制定未来和平谈判的方案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/ukraine-open-to-see-russia-at-next-summit-zelenskiy-key-aide-yermak-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 08:45:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>金正恩誓言“无条件”支持普京解决乌克兰战争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/kim-pledges-to-unconditionally-support-putin-on-war-in-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[朝鲜领导人金正恩在平壤与俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京会谈时承诺“无条件支持”俄罗斯入侵乌克兰，会谈强调深化两国关系，因美国担心向克里姆林宫的战争机器提供武器。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/kim-pledges-to-unconditionally-support-putin-on-war-in-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 07:01:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国无家可归者人数上升，住房问题成为选民关注的焦点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/rising-uk-homelessness-keeps-housing-crunch-in-front-of-voters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国无家可归人口激增已成为住房危机的另一个症状，住房危机在下个月大选之前将这一问题推上了政治议程，活动人士表示，主要政党在提供可负担住房方面做得不够。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/rising-uk-homelessness-keeps-housing-crunch-in-front-of-voters</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
